configList.render:
<a-filter
      v-show="showSearch"
      v-hasPermi="'management:role:query'"
      :model="filterParams"
      :on-query="() => ac.handlePage(filterParams, true)"
    >
      <el-form-item
        v-for="item in FilterField"
        :key="item.prop"
        :label="item.title"
        :prop="item.prop"
      >
        <a-input v-model="filterParams[item.prop]" />
      </el-form-item>
    </a-filter>

configList.Code: const { loading, filterParams, paging, showSearch, dataSource, ac } = useHook()

configList.render:
<a-page-table
      :loading="loading"
      :columns="Columns"
      :data="dataSource"
      :paging="paging"
      @pagination="ac.pagination"
    >
      <a-button
        permission="management:role:add"
        data-type="add"
        @click="dialogAc.onCreate"
      />
      <a-right-toolbar
        v-model:showSearch="showSearch"
        v-hasPermi="'management:role:query'"
        @refresh="ac.handlePage(filterParams)"
      />
      <template #actions="{ row }">
        <a-button
          v-if="row.code !=='admin'"
          permission="management:role:edit"
          data-type="edit"
          :click="() => dialogAc.onEdit(row)"
        />
        <a-button
          v-if="row.code !== 'admin'"
          permission="management:role:delete"
          data-type="del"
          :click="() => ac.handleDel(row)"
        />
      </template>
    </a-page-table>
